data.description: ENCHANTED ESTATES SUBDIVISION! This beautiful home is located in the highly desirable Enchanted Estates Subdivision inside Loop 304 in Crockett, TX! With three bedrooms and two baths, this brick home is a must see if you’re looking to be close to all the conveniences of being in the city limits. Upon entering the foyer, guests will take note of the spacious living room with cathedral ceiling, gas fireplace, and attached office space. The open concept kitchen displays nice stainless-steel appliances, black granite countertops, and ample storage space. Inside the large master bedroom, is his and her closets and a small study space that can be utilized for another home office, especially if you work from home! The private bath displays a walk-in tile shower, his and her sinks, along with a garden tub to relax after a long day. In the backyard, guests will take note of its large area for kids to play and the privacy fence around its perimeter. So, whether you’re looking for a first-time home purchase or a quiet place to retire, give us a call today to schedule a showing while this property is still available.
